dc_title_s: La principauté d'Orange et comitat de Venaissin.; La principavté d'Orange et comtat de Venaissin
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. North oriented to bottom of map. Includes dedication to Prince Frederic Henry by Jodocus and Henricus Hondius. From "Atlantis maioris appendix", Johannes Janssonius, 1630. 1 map; 38 x 50 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664.,Hondius, Hendrik, 1597-1651, cartographer.,Hondius, Jodocus, 1594 or 1595-1629, cartographer.,Hamersveldt, Everard Symonsz, 1591-1653, engraver.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner.,Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Atlantis Maioris Appendix, 1630.
